N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 1260.4 - Fees

State Regulations

The State Fire Prevention and Building Code Council may
charge fees of $400 for each new application and $200 for each renewal
application for a certificate of acceptability. Notes
